{
  "title": "Creamy Canadian Seaweed Chowder",
  "description": "A hearty, earthy, and juicy Canadian dish featuring dasima-kombu seaweed, perfect for a lazy Sunday, with an al-dente finish and jain-friendly ingredients.",
