  "instructions": [
    "Rehydrate the dasima-kombu seaweed according to package instructions and set aside.",
    "In a large pot, saute the onion, garlic, carrot, and celery in a little bit of water until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the diced potato, rehydrated seaweed, and vegetable broth to the pot, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat and let simmer for 20 minutes or until the potato is al-dente.",
    "Use an immersion blender to puree the soup until it is slightly smooth.",
    "Stir in the coconut cream and let heat through.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste, if desired.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
  ],
